weka.classifiers.collective.trees.model

Class DecisionTreeModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.tree.DefaultTreeModel
      • weka.classifiers.collective.trees.model.DecisionTreeModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.tree.TreeModel
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CollectiveTreeModel

    public class DecisionTreeModel
extends javax.swing.tree.DefaultTreeModel
implements java.io.Serializable
    A generic class for storing a decision tree model. It extends the default tree model with some WEKA specific methods and fields.
    Version:
    $Revision: 2019 $
    Author:
    FracPete (fracpete at waikato dot ac dot nz)
